<div class="container">
<h1 data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">在掌握了龙龟养殖十四步（<a class="normal_text_link" target="_blank" style="visibility: visible;" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzM2ODE4Mg==&amp;mid=2458927912&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b6dc17dc1eb63d116b5988e2afd3d695&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="养小龙虾🦞（work buddy）攻略九：龙龟养殖十四步法" data-itemshowtype="0" linktype="text" data-linktype="2">养小龙虾🦞（work buddy）攻略九：龙龟养殖十四步法</a>）法的基础上，我们开始对龙龟进行自主进化。</span></h1><h1 data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></h1><h1 data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">别再写“万能提示词”了！这位AI智能体设计师，给每个岗位配了“私人定制”方案</span></h1><blockquote><p><span leaf="">同一个提示词，市场总监和财务总监用起来效果天差地别。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">问题不在AI，在于——你的提示词没有“性格”。</span></p></blockquote><p><span leaf="">你是不是也有这样的经历？</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1"><li><section><span leaf="">写了一个提示词，AI给出的回答大而空，完全没法用。</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">同样的提示词，今天用和明天用，输出质量忽高忽低。</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">想让AI帮你做专业分析，结果它连你的行业背景都不懂。</span></section></li></ul><p><span leaf="">为什么？</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">因为99%的提示词都是“一刀切”。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">把市场总监和财务总监塞进同一个提示词框架里，用一样的语气、一样的结构、一样的指令——AI当然只能给出“平均化”的回答。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">就像让木匠和会计师用同一套工具，怎么可能顺手？</span></p><h2><span leaf="">通用提示词的三大死穴</span></h2><p><span leaf="">❌&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">大而空，全而无用</span></strong><span leaf="">&nbsp;→ 没有行业背景，没有角色定位。</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">❌&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">质量不稳定</span></strong><span leaf="">&nbsp;→ 没锁定思维模式，今天输出A，明天输出B。</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">❌&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">不懂你</span></strong><span leaf="">&nbsp;→ 既不理解岗位，也不理解性格，更不理解任务场景。</span></p><p><span leaf="">别急，今天要介绍的&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">岗位智能体 v2.0</span></strong><span leaf="">，就是来终结这个局面的。</span></p><h2><span leaf="">六维框架：给AI装上一双“识人”的眼睛</span></h2><p><span leaf="">不是简单问“你是做什么的”，而是深入六个维度，直接给AI装上识人术：</span></p><p><strong><span leaf="">行业 × 企业 × 岗位 × 性格 × 任务 × 模型</span></strong></p><table><thead><tr><th><section><span leaf="">维度</span></section></th><th><section><span leaf="">具体含义</span></section></th><th><section><span leaf="">实例</span></section></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><section><span leaf="">行业</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">你所在的赛道</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">餐饮、科技、教育、金融</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">企业</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">公司的基因</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">初创 vs 上市公司，策略完全不同</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">岗位</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">你的角色定位</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">市场总监要“冲”，财务总监要“守”</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">性格</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">你的五行人格</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">金木水火土，适配不同的AI协作模式</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">任务</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">你要解决的问题</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">用户增长、风险控制、产品创新</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">模型</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">你用什么思维框架</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">GROW、OKR、第一性原理</span></section></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span leaf="">六层叠加，生成的就是一个“懂你”的提示词。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">不再是通用模板，而是为你量身定制的AI搭档。</span></p><h2><span leaf="">最大杀器：五行人格适配</span></h2><p><span leaf="">这是岗位智能体最独特的设计——把五行人格心理学融入提示词工程。</span></p><p><span leaf="">你是什么性格，AI就用什么方式跟你协作：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1"><li><section><span leaf="">🌳&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">木行人</span></strong><span leaf="">（创新、生发）→ AI做“共创伙伴”：洞察、启发、融合</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">🔥&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">火行人</span></strong><span leaf="">（热情、行动）→ AI做“高效助理”：透视、阐释、推演</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">🪨&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">土行人</span></strong><span leaf="">（稳定、执行）→ AI做“学习伙伴”：剖析、解构、溯源</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">⚔️&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">金行人</span></strong><span leaf="">（精准、决策）→ AI做“共创导师”：思辨、推演、解构</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">🌊&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">水行人</span></strong><span leaf="">（灵活、策略）→ AI做“未知探索”：洞察、溯源、映射</span></section></li></ul><p><span leaf="">这不是玄学，是认知科学。</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">不同性格接收信息、做决策、执行任务的方式完全不同。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">岗位智能体做的事情就是——</span><strong><span leaf="">用AI的语言，匹配人的思维。</span></strong></p><h2><span leaf="">双模式：一个人用，给AI用，一鱼两吃</span></h2><p><span leaf="">v2.0 最重磅的升级：一套输入，两套产出。</span></p><p><strong><span leaf="">👤 模式A：提示词模式（给人用）</span></strong><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">完整的提示词文本 + 工作流拆解 + 指标体系 + 风险控制 + 人机协同建议。</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">→ 适合企业给员工设计AI助手、团队引入AI工作流。</span></p><p><strong><span leaf="">🐉 模式B：龙爪模式（给WorkBuddy造AI智能体）</span></strong><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">输出完整的SKILL.md文件：核心定位、7步操作流程、理论体系、标签系统、资产引用路径、自动触发规则（.mdc）。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">→ 适合为AI平台构建可自主运行的AI智能体，从设计到部署一步到位。</span></p><p><span leaf="">一个系统，两套产出。不管你是在给“人”设计工具，还是在给“AI”设计工具，都能搞定。</span></p><h2><span leaf="">10项认知指令：精细操控AI的“思维开关”</span></h2><p><span leaf="">岗位智能体内置了&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">11个AI增强关键词</span></strong><span leaf="">（官方叫“10项”，实际是11个，每个都是大脑的专属遥控器）：</span></p><table><thead><tr><th><section><span leaf="">指令</span></section></th><th><section><span leaf="">功能</span></section></th><th><section><span leaf="">适用场景</span></section></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><section><span leaf="">洞察</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">深入本质</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">需求分析、问题诊断</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">剖析</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">拆解要素</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">复杂问题分解</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">透视</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">透过现象看本质</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">根因分析、趋势判断</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">阐释</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">全面展开</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">概念传达、方案说明</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">推演</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">逻辑预测</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">方案评估、风险预测</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">解构</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">拆为基本元素</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">流程优化、系统重构</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">思辨</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">批判性分析</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">决策分析、方案对比</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">溯源</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">追根溯源</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">历史分析、根因挖掘</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">融合</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">整合不同领域</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">跨界创新、综合方案</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">启发</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">开拓新思路</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">创意激发、突破瓶颈</span></section></td></tr><tr><td><section><span leaf="">映射</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">框架转化</span></section></td><td><section><span leaf="">知识迁移、方案套用</span></section></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span leaf="">初级任务用1-2个，中级3-4个，高级5个以上。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><strong><span leaf="">像遥控器一样精确调节AI的思考方式。</span></strong></p><h2><span leaf="">自动资产引用 + Rule生成：从设计到上线一步到位</span></h2><p><span leaf="">这是龙爪模式独有的硬实力：</span></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1"><li><p><strong><span leaf="">Step 7 资产引用</span></strong><span leaf="">：不用手动翻文件夹，系统自动识别场景并填入引用路径。</span></p></li><ul class="list-paddingleft-1"><li><section><span leaf="">五行类 → 自动引用五行总智能体、凤心OS</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">餐饮类 → 自动引用味藏顶层设计</span></section></li><li><section><span leaf="">沟通类 → 自动引用凤爪OS、心文化</span></section></li></ul><li><p><strong><span leaf="">Step 8 Rule生成</span></strong><span leaf="">：连触发条件都帮你写好。上下文感知 + 直接触发词 + 场景信号，关联Skills路径，上线即用。</span></p></li></ul><h2><span leaf="">它解决了什么问题？</span></h2><p><span leaf="">如果你属于以下任何一类，岗位智能体就是为你准备的：</span></p><p><span leaf="">✅ 企业主 —— 想给每个部门的员工配AI助手，但不知从何下手。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">✅ 团队负责人 —— 团队用了AI但效果很差，因为提示词太“通用”。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">✅ AI产品经理 —— 正在构建岗位级AI智能体，需要标准化生产流程。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">✅ WorkBuddy用户 —— 想造自己的龙爪，却不知道SKILL.md怎么写。</span></p><p><strong><span leaf="">它不是一个提示词模板，而是一个提示词工厂。</span></strong><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">输入你的六维信息，输出精准适配的AI方案。</span></p><h2><span leaf="">写在最后</span></h2><p><span leaf="">AI时代，最大的浪费不是算力，而是提示词的质量。 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">一个“懂你”的提示词和一个“通用”的提示词，产出差距可能是10倍。</span></p><p><span leaf="">岗位智能体 v2.0 想做的事很简单：</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><strong><span leaf="">让每一个岗位，都拥有专属的AI助手。</span></strong></p><p><span leaf="">—— 如果这篇文章对你有启发，欢迎&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf="">点赞 + 转发 + 收藏</span></strong><span leaf="">，让更多朋友拥有专属AI搭档。</span><span leaf=""><br  /></span><span leaf="">也欢迎在评论区聊聊：你最想给哪个岗位定制提示词？遇到了什么痛点？我们评论区见！</span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p><em><span leaf="">岗位智能体 v2.0 | 维护者：龙龟神将 | 版本：2026-05-18</span></em></p><section data-layout-id="79" style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">第一步：读一读你的"类型解读"</span></span></section><section data-layout-id="80" style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span leaf="">测完之后，你会得到一份专属类型解读——包括你的核心特质、顺境/逆境表现、适合的工作、容易犯的错误、改善方法。</span></section><section data-layout-id="85" style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf="">添加<span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">姜老师微信：13224763245，电话微信同步。（备注：五行测评）</span></span></section><p><em><span leaf=""><img data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/oR040ONTeMDeXmXjicjXHPaCiaVclFgDRoog4PMOywVN6ZRiaZLEs7U1NFqvHfNUHdyto3lzXGQuZw2TK7HQ9icJreZcxqyW3JHvq4aGibrbwxPw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;watermark=1&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=0" alt="图片" class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.113888888888889" data-w="1080" data-aistatus="1"  /></span></em></p><section data-layout-id="105" style="font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">以观其妙书院</span></span></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">使命：</span>以文载道，赋能超级个体。</span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">愿景：</span>超级个体信赖的古今智慧融合平台</span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">价值观：</span>融古通今、观微知著、知行合一、妙启心智、博采精进</span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">研究方向：</span>企业文化、五行人格心理学、AI应用、象思维及思想模型、心文化</span></p><p><em><span leaf=""><img data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/oR040ONTeMBHhmqPpDEV0AtCLX5LKfPUnPYQwedICD8RP79waVL8DuJFvlsvVvJib4XloTgsIeACaVnokVqYN0EpRobgvAsbnjVDbjGrfeWo/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;watermark=1&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=1" alt="图片" class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.0027777777777778" data-w="1080" data-aistatus="2"  /></span></em></p><p><em><span leaf=""><br  /></span></em></